description: In this Workshop session, you will learn to create a spotlight on a normal website. This spotlight section includes a header section in which a logo is placed, background image, h1, h2 and a paragraph.

title: Article website
description: In this workshop, you need to create an article page. This page may contain an image section, a title and a paragraph related to it. The paragraph should contain some elements of bold words, italic words and bold-italics words.
